snippet.title: 'Top tier troll': Amber Heard names new dog Barnaby Joyce
snippet.description:
Amber Heard naming her new dog Barnaby Joyce is "top tier troll", says Reporter Eliza Barr.

It comes as Johnny Depp’s ex-wife Amber Heard named her new dog Barnaby Joyce in honour of Australia's Deputy Prime Minister and National’s leader.

The new name follows the 2015 stoush between Mr Joyce and the-then married couple of Johnny Depp and Heard.

"I actually think Barnaby is an excellent name for a dog and it's funny as well," Ms Barr said.

"It's funny as well – it's one of the great jokes of this rather miserable year I think."
